          TerraLib Application Framework for Qt
          =====================================
          
This folder contains an implementation of a simple application
framework over Qt. Basically, this framework is used by INPE's
applications (TerraView, TerraAmazon and TerraMA2) to share
and reuse components connection and to help to control
the application life cycle (startup of plugins, singnals/slots, menus
toolbars).

Dependencies:
-------------

This module requires others in order to be built:
1. Common Runtime
2. Plugin
3. Qt::Widgets

The third-party software needed:
1. Qt (QCore, QGui)

More Information:
-----------------

The TerraLib 5 wiki contains a complete explanation about
the internals of this framework:
http://www.dpi.inpe.br/terralib5/wiki/doku.php?id=wiki:designimplementation:qt::af


